e/1300203/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1300203-3.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "comment_time": "2014-04-26", "content": "<span class=\"short\">羽绒被和雨敲打在铁皮屋顶上的声音。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1257675222", "nick_name": "GINI", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/beautifulvoice/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u58226389-14.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "comment_time": "2017-10-16", "content": "<span class=\"short\">小时候读这本书，第一次感受到种族歧视的可怕，当时真是深深地同情故事里的黑人兄弟姐妹们。这本书给我幼小的心灵种下一颗人人平等的种子，但是还没等发芽就被我铲掉了。。。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "528556250", "nick_name": "陶岑", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/3074231/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3074231-22.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "comment_time": "2012-05-06", "content": "<span class=\"short\">很想很想买回来再度~重拾小学时候读的记忆~</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "1366969574", "nick_name": "废柴白", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/41600321/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u41600321-2.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar40 rating", "comment_time": "2018-05-01", "content": "<span class=\"short\">小学暑假常去同学家玩，有一天她不在家，她的妈妈给了我这本书让我回家看。回想起来我从同学那里借过很多好书，这就是其中一本。我很感谢她的母亲让我有了阅读的爱好。</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "58734328", "nick_name": "Andimio", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/2891557/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2891557-2.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "comment_time": "2008-09-09", "content": "<span class=\"short\">同《自由人》一样，《黑色棉花田》也深刻讨论了发生在那个年代的黑人问题，只是这一次，解决的方式是武力……</span>\n            "}, {"comment_id": "288284559", "nick_name": "方药雨", "user_url": "https://www.douban.com/people/34863839/", "head_image": "https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u34863839-3.jpg", "use_num": "0", "comment_score": "user-stars allstar50 rating", "co